{{For|the [[Dark Souls III]] variant|Bellowing Dragoncrest Ring (Dark Souls III)}}
The '''Bellowing Dragoncrest Ring''' is a [[Rings (Dark Souls)|ring]] in ''[[Dark Souls]]''.

{{Description
|First paragraph  = A special ring granted to only the most accomplished sorcerers at the Vinheim Dragon School.
|Second paragraph = The ring is engraved with an everlasting dragon, and boosts the strength of sorceries.}}

==Effect==
Increases [[Sorcery (Dark Souls)|sorcery]] and [[Pyromancy (Dark Souls)|pyromancy]] damage by roughly 20%. It does not increase the damage of magical weapon [[Weapon Augmentation|buffs]] such as [[Magic Weapon]].

